    "title": "Looking for Real Estate Agent at JLL India",
    "description": "Are you a skilled Real Estate Agent looking for your next big career move? JLL India in Kochi offers you the perfect platform to grow professionally and personally.\n\nAbout JLL India:\nJLL India is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Source and close property deals with prospective buyers and investors\n• Maintain a pipeline of qualified leads using CRM software\n• Manage RERA documentation and compliance requirements\n• Manage relationships with existing customers post-purchase\n• Conduct site visits and property presentations for clients\n• Achieve monthly and quarterly sales targets\n• Provide advisory services on property investment and market trends\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Any graduate with relevant experience\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Market Research\n• Proficiency in Property Valuation\n• Proficiency in Property Management\n• Proficiency in Portfolio Management\n• Proficiency in Project Management\n• Proficiency in CRM Software\n• Proficiency in Negotiation Skills\n• Proficiency in Real Estate Law\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Kochi, Kerala, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with JLL India!",
